{"tid":1402324,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（文宣入嚟）我係文宣，你係文宣，個個都係文宣啊","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:38:57.000Z","uid":197980,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c613a9251dd80bb6291b5bc0e674ce9a85f937e","tid":1402324,"uid":197980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:05:48.000Z","msg":"對於前線行動升級，我覺得文宣都要與時並進，帶翻淺黃、中立，乃到係淺藍嘅人接受，接受唔到都要諒解。<br />\n<br />\n對付唔同立場嘅人就要用唔同方法，淺黃可以温和啲，對付藍就要無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拋磚：<br />\nQ) 淺黃老豆個先睇直播話放火好危險<br />\nA1)我答：個少少火，你拜山燒元寶蠟燭仲大火啦。<br />\n<br />\n但萬一對象係藍或者中立就要屈轉頭，要用更無恥，更恥嘅手法，話係對家嘅錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA2)梗係因為出催淚彈啲火舌點着咗啲紙啦，警察又亂放彈。而家火燭啦，開心啦，又麻煩到消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他Possible嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n1）警察打份工啫，唔洗打佢哋嘅。<br />\n2）出晒full gear仲唔係早有預謀要打人？<br />\n3）嘩，有武器庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎其他問題<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 教化身邊嘅人都係文宣一種，唔好成日叫文宣幫手，你自己都係文宣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce588a8ce3b4729cbec89d530e966ca04c01d5d","tid":1402324,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c727f7464f6bf3e293e996324ab626580684d34c","tid":1402324,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:06:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06224b274c079544f1b1c480219a5e3d28c0a724","tid":1402324,"uid":197980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":